<plot>While on their way to compete in a kung fu competition four friends are told the story of how a dozen students from their university had died while en route to the same competition 30 years ago. Thinking that the Krishnas who had told them the tale were just telling a ghost story to scare them the kids set off down a dark country lane. Along the way they encounter the zombies and are forced to hide in an abandoned farmhouse. There they must fend off the zombies using their martial arts training and four very magical rings.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?179237</url></doc>
